{"id":205,"date":"2018-06-16T00:41:45","date_gmt":"2018-06-15T17:41:45","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/toyota3.w2steam.com\/?p=205"},"modified":"2021-05-19T22:46:46","modified_gmt":"2021-05-19T15:46:46","slug":"do-doi-mau-noi-that-doc-dao-cho-cac-dong-xe-cao-cap","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/do-doi-mau-noi-that-doc-dao-cho-cac-dong-xe-cao-cap\/","title":{"rendered":"Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd ra m\u1eaft b\u1ed9 3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb: Wigo, Rush v\u00e0 Avanza"},"content":{"rendered":"<h1 class=\"entry-title rs post-title\"><a href=\"http:\/\/giaxetoyotaphutho.com.vn\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd<\/strong><\/span><\/a> ra m\u1eaft b\u1ed9 3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb: Wigo, Rush v\u00e0 Avanza<\/h1>\n<div class=\"box-single\">\n<div class=\"post-thumb\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" src=\"https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rush-avanza-wigo.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rush-avanza-wigo.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rush-avanza-wigo-300x254.jpg 300w, https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/rush-avanza-wigo-768x649.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"845\" \/><\/div>\n<div class=\"content-post\">\n<h4><strong><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\">Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd<\/span><\/strong> ra m\u1eaft b\u1ed9 3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb: Wigo, Rush v\u00e0 Avanza<\/h4>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea1i L\u00fd Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft 3 m\u1eabu xe nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bao g\u1ed3m: Toyota Wigo, Avanza v\u00e0 Rush. C\u1ea3 3 m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb Indonesia v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam (TMV) tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 9\/2018<\/p>\n<h5><a href=\"http:\/\/giaxetoyotaphutho.com.vn\/cua-hang\/wigo-1-2g-at\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Toyota Wigo<\/span><\/a>\u00a0\u2013 B\u1eaft tr\u1ecdn nh\u1ecbp vui<\/h5>\n<p>C\u00e1i t\u00ean Wigo b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \u201cWe go\u201d th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng linh ho\u1ea1t nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho m\u1ecdi kh\u00e1ch hang, Wigo n\u1eb1m trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Morning v\u00e0 i10<\/p>\n<p>Wigo S\u1edf h\u1eefu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe kho\u1eafn, kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c con ph\u1ed1 nh\u1ecf, m\u1eabu xe Wigo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 thu nh\u1eadp \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean di chuy\u1ec3n trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 3660mm, r\u1ed9ng 1600mm v\u00e0 cao 1520mm, ngo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh xe Wigo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi \u0111\u00e8n tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u1ea1ng b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfu, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p d\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e8n LED \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb, \u0111\u00e8n s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9, v\u00e0nh xe h\u1ee3p kim nh\u00f4m th\u1ec3 thao. Nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau, chi\u1ebfc xe c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u00f3 ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED.<\/p>\n<p>Wigo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 06 m\u00e0u tr\u1ebb trung l\u00e0: \u0110en (X13), X\u00e1m (1G3), \u0110\u1ecf (R40), B\u1ea1c (1E7), Tr\u1eafng (W09), Cam (R71)<\/p>\n<p><strong>Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n 345 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n MT v\u00e0 405 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n AT.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4><a href=\"http:\/\/giaxetoyotaphutho.com.vn\/cua-hang\/toyota-avanza-1-5g-at\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Toyota Avanza<\/span><\/a>\u00a0\u2013 Mang y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho m\u1ed7i h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh<\/h4>\n<p>Toyota Avanza l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe 7 ch\u1ed7 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb ngang v\u1edbi\u00a0<a title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/vios-2018\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Toyota Vios\u00a0<\/a>Th\u1ea7n Th\u00e1nh .Avanza c\u00f3 2 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 1.3 MT gi\u00e1 537 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n 1.5 AT gi\u00e1 593 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.\u00a0Avanza l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe MPV gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Toyota. M\u1eabu xe Avanza v\u1edbi v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n tinh t\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed9ng cho 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0ng tin c\u1eady cho c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Toyota Avanza ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 phanh ABS v\u00e0 2 t\u00fai kh\u00ed. Gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i b\u00ean trong khoang cabin b\u1ecdc n\u1ec9, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9nh tay. H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf ph\u00eda sau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eadp g\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ec3 gia t\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ed3. Xe c\u00f3 7 ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i. Xe c\u00f3 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1. \u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 4 xy-lanh, dung t\u00edch 1.3L, cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 94 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 121 Nm. H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 s\u00e0n 5 c\u1ea5p. \u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 4 xy-lanh, dung t\u00edch 1.5L, cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 102 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn 136 Nm. H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 4 c\u1ea5p. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0u xe Avanza c\u00f3 06 m\u00e0u bao g\u1ed3m: \u0110en (X12), Ghi (1G3), Champagne (T23), B\u1ea1c (1E7), Xanh (8X2) v\u00e0 Tr\u1eafng (W09)<\/p>\n<h4><a href=\"http:\/\/giaxetoyotaphutho.com.vn\/cua-hang\/rush-1-5-at\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Toyota Rush<\/span><\/a> \u2013\u00a0S\u0103n th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c, t\u00ecm l\u1ed1i ri\u00eang<\/h4>\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i T\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n mong mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb. C\u0169ng gi\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0 Wigo v\u00e0 Avanza, Rush \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n cho c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Phillipines, Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-2453\" src=\"https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20181001_142653-1024x576.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20181001_142653-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20181001_142653-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/toyotamydinh247.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/20181001_142653-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Toyota Rush s\u1edf h\u1eefu phong c\u00e1ch sang tr\u1ecdng, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao v\u1edbi 7 ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh, trang b\u1ecb an to\u00e0n t\u1ed1i ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n 5 sao ASEAN NCAP ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh y\u00eau th\u00edch m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe SUV r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Toyota Rush \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ed nh\u01b0 \u201cti\u1ec3u Fortuner\u201d. M\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n 668 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n<p>Ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i mang phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 thao, \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Toyota nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Toyota Rush c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0 phanh ABS, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c, camera l\u00f9i, c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed7 xe v\u00e0 6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed.<\/p>\n<p>Toyota Rush c\u00f3 06 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn bao g\u1ed3m: \u0110\u1ecf (3Q3), B\u1ea1c (1E7), \u0110\u1ecf (R54), \u0110en (X12), \u0110\u1ed3ng (4T3) v\u00e0 Tr\u1eafng (W09)<\/p>\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, th\u1eeba h\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i c\u1ee7a Toyota l\u00e0 Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n, \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady, Wigo, Avanza v\u00e0 Rush h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi thu nh\u1eadp \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua xe l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y y\u00ean t\u00e2m trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<h4><em>M\u1ecdi thong tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 <strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">hotline : 098 2283 444 \u2013 0816 022 999<\/span><\/strong> Ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch kinh doanh <a href=\"http:\/\/giaxetoyotaphutho.com.vn\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd.<\/strong><\/span><\/a><\/em><\/h4>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd ra m\u1eaft b\u1ed9 3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb: Wigo, Rush v\u00e0 Avanza Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd ra m\u1eaft b\u1ed9 3 \u00f4 t\u00f4 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb: Wigo, Rush v\u00e0 Avanza \u0110\u1ea1i L\u00fd Toyota Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft 3 m\u1eabu xe nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, bao g\u1ed3m: Toyota Wigo,&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":712,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=205"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1001,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/205\/revisions\/1001"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/712"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=205"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/toyota2.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/